1. File & Directory Management (Navigating servers and Managing deployment files)

ls        # list files
ls -l     # detailed view
ls -a     # hidden files
cd        # change directory
pwd       # present working directory
mkdir     # create directory
rm -rf    # delete files/folders
cp        # copy files
mv        # move/rename
touch     # create file
stat      # file details
tree      # folder structure

2. File Viewing & Editing  {Reading logs (tail -f /var/log/app.log) Editing configs in /etc}

cat       # view file
less      # scroll file
head      # first lines
tail      # last lines
tail -f   # live logs 
nano      # simple editor
vim       # advanced editor (important)

3. Searching & Filtering

grep      # search text
grep -i   # case insensitive
grep -r   # recursive
find      # find files
locate    # quick search
which     # command path
whereis   # binary + source

